graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:AdminCreateAttachmentLibraryInput!)
{
	adminCreateAttachmentLibrary (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		name
		pathname
		filename
		url
		mime
		extension
		size
		width
		height
		data
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	adminGetAttachmentLibraries (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		pathname
		filename
		url
		mime
		extension
		size
		width
		height
		data
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
